Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.61,0:00:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Under Grandma's orders, we went to a place far away from the town.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.41,0:00:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A Duel Lodge!?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a wise old man trained in the\N art of Duel Training was waiting for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.20,0:00:22.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And me and the old man has a statue duel with the legendary monsters.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.06,0:00:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But for some reason, I've become a Monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.69,0:00:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think I may have just learned something...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But now I have to win against the old man's disciple in a duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.87,0:00:41.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll fight too, Yuma.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.14,0:00:45.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't forgive anyone who insults the old man, even if he's a fellow disciple!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.06,0:00:48.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to em'!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.36,0:01:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set 2 cards face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.31,0:01:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and my monsters no... my friends will definitely win against you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.07,0:01:18.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Something a kid carved by light would say.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.18,0:01:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. My master taught you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:24.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then let me show you the gap between light and darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.27,0:01:26.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness overcomes the light!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.58,0:01:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hang in there, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:32.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this duel is kinda scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.41,0:01:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's being consumed by the darkness more and more...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.43,0:01:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.88,0:01:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.04,0:01:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By decreasing it's attack power by 500 points,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.62,0:01:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon this monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come! Dododo Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.13,0:01:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Filling up your field, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.95,0:02:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you had released Gagaga Magician and summoned Dododo Warrior,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.06,0:02:06.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's attack power would've been higher than Blade Heart's.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.11,0:02:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why did Yuma decrease Dododo Warrior's attack power, instead of using Gagaga Magician?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure Yuma has...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.50,0:02:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, are you still trying to protect you monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.76,0:02:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have any problem with that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.86,0:02:21.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nope.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.77,0:02:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here I go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.70,0:02:27.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand I activate the Magic Card, Instant Blow of Friendship!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.61,0:02:31.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a monster on my field battles,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.27,0:02:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,none of us take the damage, but it destroys the opponent's monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.24,0:02:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dododo Warrior attacks Armored Ninja Brave Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go! Dododo Axe!!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.13,0:02:46.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permanent Trap open!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.28,0:02:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Ninjitsu Arts: Freeze Lock!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:52.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a "Ninja" is on my field,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.97,0:02:55.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It ends the opponent's monster's attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.59,0:02:58.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and as long as this Permanent Trap exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.77,0:03:02.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,your monsters can't change their battle positions.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.49,0:03:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's how it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.66,0:03:06.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.00,0:03:10.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't afford to lose this duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.65,0:03:19.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.79,0:03:22.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}they're all ingredients to color each day. \NDon't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.89,0:03:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:37.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The truth is, I was lonely. Until I met you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.37,0:03:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I lied to myself that being alone was easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.15,0:03:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My favorite books and hobbies,\N they don't seem to match.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.55,0:03:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You were the only one to nod in agreement with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:57.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Happiness and sadness and anger and\N Do and Re and Mi and Fa and So and La and Ti and Do,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.56,0:03:59.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It doesn't work unless they're different,\N the harmony and the scenario.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.30,0:04:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one is exactly the same,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.60,0:04:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}because that's the reason for living.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:12.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if the sounds are dissonant from time to time,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.07,0:04:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}don't give up on the strength that will get you through.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.31,0:04:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When we reach the edge of the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.38,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the view we see will be the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whether it's rainy, or windy,\N or a cold winter blizzard, or the burning sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.36,0:04:32.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all ingredients to color each day.\N Don't lose heart, will or love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}the kindness you gave me was strict,\N when we clashed I learned irritation.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It starts by recognizing our differences, dancing freely,\N the creation of Heaven and Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.98,0:04:56.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:59.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(452,520)}" Numbers 16: The Deadliest Ninja Arts!\N The Most Terrifying Ninja!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.07,0:04:59.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.25,0:05:02.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my hand I activate Spy Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.14,0:05:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By sending a monster from my hand to the cemetery,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.67,0:05:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can destroy a set card on your field!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.19,0:05:12.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Ninja Aqua!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.92,0:05:15.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Putting your own life on the line, invade enemy territory!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.62,0:05:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eradicate his set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sacrifices his monsters for just one chance to win.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.00,0:05:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how he duels.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.62,0:05:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.82,0:05:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.53,0:05:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh Yuma, so your already dueling here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roku-{\i1}san{\i0}, did you teach him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.03,0:05:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haru-{\i1}san{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.28,0:05:44.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.79,0:05:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His sister too!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.85,0:05:49.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just as I thought, you do duel, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.16,0:05:50.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.13,0:05:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, your gonna get...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.99,0:05:54.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:58.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child is attempting to surpass himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.71,0:06:00.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The person he's been up until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.05,0:06:03.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just believe in him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.32,0:06:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.93,0:06:08.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sister...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.26,0:06:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep focusing, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.94,0:06:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you've got a crowd to witness your death?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.51,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'm going to show them your death!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.09,0:06:20.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Heart attacks Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:22.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sudden Rapid...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.40,0:06:23.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Strike!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.49,0:06:28.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Strike all standing in your way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.06,0:06:30.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By detaching an Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.77,0:06:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It can attack the opponent's monster once more!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blade Heart attacks Dododo Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.34,0:06:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your face-down card is Gagaga Back.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.81,0:06:46.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By losing 600 points of your life,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.93,0:06:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has an effect to revive a monster.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.84,0:06:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you still trying to protect your monsters at all costs!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.57,0:06:56.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,600 for just 1?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.35,0:06:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any meaning in reviving the monster?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.08,0:07:05.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let this revival damage the fool even more!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.42,0:07:08.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Permanent Trap open! Armored Ninjitsu Arts: Last Mist!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.44,0:07:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have a "Ninja", all ll Special Summoned monsters on the opponent's field have their attack power halved!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.99,0:07:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on, save your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.81,0:07:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even knowing you're only increasing your terrible situation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.88,0:07:27.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, ignore him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.54,0:07:29.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stick to your own thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.56,0:07:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fight with your own feelings!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.11,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely at what your teacher has taught you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.12,0:07:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There must be a secret method to win beyond it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.76,0:07:40.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That is what I wish to see.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.49,0:07:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Astral...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.18,0:07:45.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Gagaga Back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.60,0:07:49.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card, if Gagaga Magician was destroyed by battle,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.23,0:07:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It will revive with it's monster friend that was destroyed by battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.80,0:08:01.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, for each monster revived I take 600 points of damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.05,0:08:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His life is at 300...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.82,0:08:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.89,0:08:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, with Armored Ninjitsu Arts: Rust Mist's effect,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.70,0:08:24.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All Special Summoned monsters on the opponent's field will have their attack power halved!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.67,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.29,0:08:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you care so much about your monster? Even though their attack powers are almost gone, and your life is depleting.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.04,0:08:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you can trust the monsters?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.61,0:08:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will believe in my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.03,0:08:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once my feelings connect to the monsters'!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.41,0:08:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They will save me for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.27,0:08:52.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean by connected?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.91,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters will save you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.84,0:08:57.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters are not your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.57,0:08:59.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They are just servants of the duelists!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.58,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had about all I could stand of that stupid nonsense about "heart"!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duels are ruled by darkness and fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.67,0:09:10.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.88,0:09:12.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what dueling is about!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.96,0:09:15.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Act arrogant and boast all you like.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.73,0:09:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your life is only at 300...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.44,0:09:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If your life reaches 0, and your friends don't save your till then,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.65,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.01,0:09:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will believe in my monsters no... my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.15,0:09:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.32,0:09:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright, it came!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.40,0:09:41.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card, Gagaga Bolt!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.42,0:09:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I have a "Gagaga" monster on my side, I can destroy a card on the opponent's field!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.40,0:09:51.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I destroy Armored Ninja Blade Heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.11,0:09:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.00,0:10:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I attack directly with Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.27,0:10:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then Dododo Warrior attacks directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.51,0:10:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,GO!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.75,0:10:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't let you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.74,0:10:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From my cemetery I activate Armored Ninja Aqua's effect!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.72,0:10:21.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By excluding this card it negated a monster's direct attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Answer me my friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.25,0:10:25.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Dododo Warrior attacks,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.29,0:10:30.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The opponent's Magic, Trap, and monster's effects are negated!.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.21,0:10:30.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.01,0:10:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now the effects of Rust Mist and Aqua are gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.08,0:10:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I can attack directly!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.33,0:10:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Dododo Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.25,0:10:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dododo Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.67,0:10:45.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.58,0:10:52.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.27,0:10:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I set a card face-down and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.13,0:11:00.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you see me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.64,0:11:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our feelings have reached our friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.60,0:11:08.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We aren't the only ones who are fighting in this duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.40,0:11:11.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My friends have answered me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.86,0:11:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what my master, Old Man Rokujuro taught me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.95,0:11:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.60,0:11:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man taught you? Yeah right!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.79,0:11:23.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have surpassed my master and that teaching
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.94,0:11:27.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have any friends, and I don't trust anyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.58,0:11:28.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fight alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And I win alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.92,0:11:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.06,0:11:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Magic Card...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.46,0:11:38.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Ninjitsu Arts: Gold Conversion!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:42.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I destroy every card with "Armored Ninjitsu Arts" in it's name!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.21,0:11:45.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's destroying his own traps?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.07,0:11:49.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I draw 2 cards from my deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.31,0:11:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.89,0:11:56.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If there's a monster on the opponent's field,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.09,0:11:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon Armored Ninja Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.50,0:12:08.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is strange...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I activate the Magic Card, Armored Ninjitsu Arts: Undead Return!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.48,0:12:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can Special Summon a "Ninja" monster that's in my cemetery!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:20.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, Armored Ninja Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.34,0:12:26.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When Flame is successfully summoned, his level goes up by 1.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.85,0:12:31.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He has a No.!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.38,0:12:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.87,0:12:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.23,0:12:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And your "master" and his "light" along with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.74,0:12:43.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I overlay the level 5 Armored Ninja Earth and Armored Ninja Flame!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.75,0:12:50.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These two monsters will construct the overlay network!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.00,0:12:52.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:55.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, No. 12!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.11,0:13:05.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armored Ninja Crimson Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.30,0:13:17.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This monsters is my true power!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness inside the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.15,0:13:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Shadow engulf him in darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.68,0:13:24.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A-A Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To come this far for the No. to come out...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.62,0:13:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, he even has a No.!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.87,0:13:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This monster is a great source of Yamikawa's darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.87,0:13:39.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.31,0:13:45.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take on the strongest Ninja attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.23,0:13:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Shadow attacks Gagaga Magician!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.22,0:13:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,T-This is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:51.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, the Trap Card!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.19,0:13:52.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.35,0:13:55.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card open, Guts Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.97,0:14:03.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With this card, the attacking monster can't attack any other monster except the one that's targeted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.03,0:14:08.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I change the attack from Gagaga Magician to Dododo Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:12.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the monster targeted by the attack can't be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.01,0:14:22.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What persistence, with this I end my turn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.63,0:14:26.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.25,0:14:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But If I'm attacked next time...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.27,0:14:33.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Put yourself together, Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.26,0:14:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time he's not dueling with full spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.33,0:14:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He might be hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.61,0:14:43.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.40,0:14:47.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, kid? Is it already over!?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.06,0:14:51.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the power of your friends that you believed in?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.50,0:14:54.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, remember that...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.84,0:14:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You and the monsters have the same feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.25,0:14:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your teacher's words!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.16,0:15:04.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.89,0:15:06.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.46,0:15:11.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know the monster's feelings they will answer you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.01,0:15:15.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those emotions will truly make the monsters move.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.01,0:15:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monster's feelings?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.64,0:15:38.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.88,0:15:39.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The monsters are...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.34,0:15:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't care if it's a No.!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.05,0:15:52.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me and my friends will get out of this trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.18,0:15:55.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.30,0:15:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your Duel Meal!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.10,0:16:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks a lot!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.22,0:16:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Kotori!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.79,0:16:08.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll bring it to em'!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.76,0:16:10.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.63,0:16:14.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It came, It came, it came!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.97,0:16:17.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic Decrease!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.02,0:16:23.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card can decrease a monster's level by 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.47,0:16:28.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I decrease Dododo Warrior's level from 6 to 4!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.30,0:16:33.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,, I overlay the level 4 Gagaga Magician and Dododo Warrior!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.80,0:16:39.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The 2 monsters will open the overlay network.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.70,0:16:41.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Xyz Summon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.59,0:16:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come, No. 39 Aspiring Emperor Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.76,0:16:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.51,0:16:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you see it now Yuma, the key to victory?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.18,0:16:55.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.47,0:16:59.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aspiring Emperor Hope attacks Crimson Shadow!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.03,0:17:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Blade Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.73,0:17:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did it, Hope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.04,0:17:25.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness shall reign!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.60,0:17:27.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson Shadow's effect activates!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.62,0:17:30.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By detaching an Overlay Unit,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.73,0:17:33.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I negate Crimson Shadow's destruction!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.52,0:17:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate the Quick-Play Magic, Revenge Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.23,0:17:47.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If a monster on our field couldn't destroy the opponent's monster in battle, Revenge Attack can be activated!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.98,0:17:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope's attack power goes up by 1000 and can battle once again!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.09,0:17:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.41,0:18:07.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this light?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.41,0:18:11.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is Aspiring Emperor Hope's strength.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.79,0:18:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Light Of Hope... Will banish the Darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.45,0:18:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hope Sword Slash!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.29,0:18:24.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness has...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.96,0:18:56.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma!\NYuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.50,0:18:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So how's that!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.78,0:19:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like Yuma's duel is always depending on his trumps!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.73,0:19:07.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So I was right about sending him to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.33,0:19:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a quick learner.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.08,0:19:13.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That child learned his strength and the fate that surrounds it.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.65,0:19:15.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was obviously going to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.69,0:19:18.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about? That was a close call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.16,0:19:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.95,0:19:20.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,About him...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Move away, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.67,0:19:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't you see it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.11,0:19:50.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This statue's wound?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.45,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The old man gave his all to fix it after you attacked it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.76,0:19:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This monster is your friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.70,0:20:02.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your important friend!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.14,0:20:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I... sought strength and power...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.55,0:20:39.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I couldn't see that in the darkness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The darkness is gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.61,0:20:46.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The rest is up to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.18,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.62,0:20:59.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamikawa wants to continue training again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.84,0:21:01.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's fight again!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.32,0:21:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This time with your monsters, no...your friends!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.12,0:21:14.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you duel after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.29,0:21:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.05,0:21:20.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just don't overdo it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.25,0:21:24.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.17,0:21:27.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.21,0:21:30.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the Duel Lodge's Hidden Deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:33.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This deck is most suited to be with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.58,0:21:36.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I bet this deck will respond to your feelings.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.13,0:21:38.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that fine?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.25,0:21:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.16,0:21:46.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.76,0:21:50.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now you'll make an impact in the World Duel Carnival with this deck!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.44,0:21:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.16,0:21:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yuma, do you plan on participating?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.97,0:21:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.90,0:21:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now I can beat any number of guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Astral?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.90,0:22:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's not here.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.23,0:22:07.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Yuma has improved.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can I....
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can I win...?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.32,0:22:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Against that Kaito?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.24,0:22:24.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time to start the duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.50,0:22:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here's this week's quiz!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.21,0:22:30.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How many cards are required in your deck?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.91,0:22:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,20, 30, or 40?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.19,0:22:44.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Today's test is hard. I can't divide myself from pleasure and temptation.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.80,0:22:49.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wanna watch TV when I get home.\N The recent anime are fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.91,0:23:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}In any case, this test is hard. \NLanguage, Math and English are especially bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.41,0:23:09.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm only average at science and social studies.\N The only thing I'm good at is P.E.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.59,0:23:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Wait up, Baby!) For who's sake...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.29,0:23:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Is that, Baby!) ...am I remembering...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.73,0:23:17.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(Just hold on, Baby!) ...the answer...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:18.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}(What are we!? Baby!) ...they wanted?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.96,0:23:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if I write the correct answer on this paper,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.70,0:23:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}in one year, in ten years, will anything change?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.44,0:23:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The world I drew in the corner of my dreams,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.54,0:23:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}one day I will race through the open sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.32,0:23:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one can blame this heart of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.19,0:23:48.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Nothing is really correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.11,0:23:52.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Numbers Club"?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.49,0:23:55.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! We're gonna investigate the secrets of the Numbers!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.37,0:23:58.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm worried about Yuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.04,0:24:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but you're going to have to give up on your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.33,0:24:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forget that!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.79,0:24:04.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is... fear?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.79,0:24:07.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need your strength anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.38,0:24:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll save everyone with my own hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.05,0:24:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time on Yu-Gi-Oh! ZeXal!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.51,0:24:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The All-Seeing Seer: The Terrifying Fortuneteller – Jin"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.51,0:24:19.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna bring it to 'em!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.93,0:24:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The answer's 40!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.81,0:24:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You need to have at least 40 cards in your deck.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:27.94,0:24:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But by adding other cards you like, you can increase your deck all the way up to 60 cards!
